entries.title_d: A Velocity mercenary flight commander has been spotted in the Dathomir system. Intercept, disable, and inspect his vessel for who ever he is getting his orders from.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Inspect the Velocity Mercenary Flight Commander
entries.quest_location_d: The commander's ship is located inside the Dathomir system. Intercept his vessel near the supplied navigation waypoint.
entries.quest_inspect_t: Inspect the Velocity Mercenary Flight Commander
entries.quest_inspect_d: Once the commander is disabled, inspect it to find out who is sending him his orders.
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the disabled commander and transfer the orders to your fighter.
